<item>
            <title>[LU-3493] Need to determine if data was affected by unreadable sectors on RAID.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3493</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One of our luns experienced unreadable sectors.  The RAID was able to report which LBAs were affected for the lun/OST.  How do we map the LBA to check if any files were affected?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>CentOS 6.3, SGI IS5500 (Netapp E5400), </environment>
        <key id="19519">LU-3493</key>
            <summary>Need to determine if data was affected by unreadable sectors on RAID.</summary>
